Class LayerInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.spatial.georaster.LayerInfo

  • public class LayerInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    LayerInfo is a Java class mapped to the XML element LayerInfo in the Oracle Spatial GeoRaster metadata.
